channel.title: Bad Source File
channel.description:
Hey guys, so I fixed all the 100 Errors in HumidityX's Source. Anyways, Im compiling and I get this last error....
starting... src\com\rs\game\player\Pets.java:12: error: cannot access Misc import com.rs.utils.Misc; ^ bad source file: src\com\rs\utils\Misc.java file does not contain class com.rs.utils.Misc Please remove or make sure it appears in the correct subdirectory of the sou rcepath. Press any key to continue . . .
I really Need Help fixing it. I may reward the Person who tells me how to fix this. Thanks guys bye!
